snippet.title: Buckshot Roulette – Coming Soon to XBOX GamePass
snippet.description:
"Face off in a high-stakes game of Russian roulette with a shotgun. Challenge the Dealer one-on-one, or go all in with friends. Four players, one survivor. Pull the trigger and test your luck.
Coming soon to PC and Xbox Game Pass.
